  * Update soversions to fix symlinks:
    - libopen-pal 20.10.0 -> 20.10.1
    - libopen-rte 20.10.0 -> 20.10.1
    - libmca_common_sm 20.10.0 -> 20.10.1
    - libmpi_mpifh 20.10.0 -> 20.11.0
    Closes: #865471, #865540
  * Fix typo in test patch for s390x

